# Summary
This documentation describes the Sleekflow destination integration for Amplitude, which allows syncing user cohorts to Sleekflow's omni-channel messaging platform for targeted communication via WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, and other channels, requiring either email or phone number as unique identifiers.

